  <h2>Lutz's local HVAC team — fluent in both Pasco and Hillsborough permitting</h2>
  <p>Lutz is one of the more unusual service areas we cover. The <strong>Pasco / Hillsborough county line</strong> cuts right through it, which means the permitting jurisdiction for your HVAC replacement depends on which side of your street you live on. We handle this every week and we know exactly which department your parcel goes through — Pasco County Building Services for 33548 and most of 33558, or Hillsborough County / City of Tampa for 33549 and parts of 33558. One less thing for you to figure out.</p>
  <p>Florida license <strong>CAC1822037</strong>, hundreds of Google reviews, and we've been driving into Lutz from our Wesley Chapel HQ for 16+ years.</p>

